# Project Summary

This project analyzes the used car market in Hyderabad using data collected
through API-based web scraping.

The goal of the project is to understand how factors such as vehicle age,
kilometers driven, brand reputation, body type, and ownership history
influence resale prices.

The project includes:

- Data collection through web scraping
- Data cleaning and preprocessing
- Feature engineering
- Exploratory Data Analysis
- Visualization of pricing trends

The insights derived from this analysis can support buyers, sellers,
and online marketplaces in understanding used car pricing behavior.
